/*
 * This Hyperlambda snippet demonstrates how to add a static integer value to an existing node's value.
 *
 * 1. [math.add]
 *    * Adds the values of its child nodes together.
 *
 * 2. [get-value:x:@.arg]
 *    * Retrieves the current value of the [.arg] node.
 *
 * 3. [.]:int:2
 *    * A static integer value to be added to the value retrieved from [.arg].
 *
 * Result:
 * * The result of [math.add] will be the sum of the current value of [.arg] and 2.
 */
math.add
   get-value:x:@.arg
   .:int:2